{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"act11d0_level_act11d0_sub-1-1_end","storyGroup":"act11d0","storySort":19,"storyDependence":"act11d0_level_act11d0_08_end","storyCanShow":1,"storyCode":"TW-S-1","storyName":"三座巨像","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"毕德曼看着门外，恐慌的感觉自内心溢出。那不是纵火犯，那只是一个可怕的提案。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"activities/act11d0/level_act11d0_sub-1-1_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"act11d0_s01","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":17,"next":19,"characters":["毕德曼","塞弗林","？？？","镇民","塔佳娜"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"九尾狐活动 支线1","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":3},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$loneliness_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/static/m_avg/m_avg_loneliness_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":7,"musicid":0},{"type":"text","text":"2:25 P.M.    天气/阴","id":8},{"type":"text","text":"莱塔尼亚境内，移动城镇沃伦姆德，议事厅临时客房","id":9},{"type":"dialog","id":10},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":12},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":13},{"type":"text","text":"......该怎么办？","id":14},{"type":"text","text":"谁能想到比起一座创造了无数经济价值的城镇，他们居然更看重一场婚礼？","id":15},{"type":"text","text":"大裂谷的损失惨重，尽管避免了人员伤亡，但是沃伦姆德失去了四分之一的面积是板上钉钉的事实......","id":16},{"type":"text","text":"......我该怎么办？","id":17},{"type":"dialog","id":18},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":19},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":20},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":21},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"0.6","id":22},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"请进。","id":24},{"type":"dialog","id":25},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":26},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":27},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":28},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......看起来，你的伤好多了。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......","id":31},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"别总是这么一副“我们全要完蛋”的表情，偶尔也该豁达一点。","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"你就安心待在这吧，议事厅的客房总不至于还有人敢来闹事。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"我的家呢？","id":36},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......惨不忍睹。你不会想知道的。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"告诉我。","id":40},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"门锁被撬了，里面被砸了个稀巴烂，除了你的保险柜基本没有什么东西是完好的。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......当然，他们你没那么好心放过你的宝贝保险柜，他们只是没有成功，上面有高温加热的痕迹。","id":43,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":44},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......随他们去吧。","id":45},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":46},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"稀奇，你对你的家很有感情？","id":47,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":48},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"怎么也是住了些年的房子......不过对你们而言，我始终是个外人。","id":49},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":50},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"别这么说......作为一座商业城镇，沃伦姆德可不会那么排外。只不过......","id":51,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":52},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"我烟味过敏。","id":53},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":54},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"啊，好。","id":55,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"但听我一句劝，你暂时就不要随便上街了。这次只是皮外伤，下一次就不好说了。","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"你知道，现在沃伦姆德没有宪兵队驻扎，塔佳娜他们顶多算是民兵团，真出了事没人管得住。","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你也做了件蠢事，塞弗林。","id":59},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......我也不知道他们一场婚礼能办这么久啊。","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"行了，好好休息，我就说这么多。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......责任不在你，我们都知道。","id":64,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":65},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"天灾无法准确预测......","id":66},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":67},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"人祸也是。","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"好了，你就安心养伤吧。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"想想之后的事情。","id":70,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":71},{"type":"character","id":72},{"type":"playsound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","volume":"0.6","id":73},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":74},{"type":"text","text":"之后的事情。","id":75},{"type":"text","text":"我已经预见到了之后的事情。","id":76},{"type":"text","text":"大裂谷完美地封死了东南方向的全部航线，沃伦姆德只能向北方继续行进。","id":77},{"type":"text","text":"......如果不能及时和其他城镇建立救援协议，冬天来临，势必会出现饥荒。","id":78},{"type":"text","text":"饥荒......","id":79},{"type":"text","text":"会死很多人，我......","id":80},{"type":"dialog","id":81},{"type":"character","id":82},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":83},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8a/Avg_bg_bg_black.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":84},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"text","text":"不，这不怪我。","id":86},{"type":"text","text":"......这不怪我。","id":87},{"type":"dialog","id":88},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":89},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":90},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":91},{"type":"text","text":"七天后","id":92},{"type":"dialog","id":93},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","id":94},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":95},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"喂~有人在吗？","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我听说沃伦姆德的天灾信使暂住在这里喔？有人吗？","id":97},{"type":"dialog","id":98},{"type":"text","text":"是没听过的声音，年轻女性。","id":99},{"type":"text","text":"她知道我是天灾信使。","id":100},{"type":"text","text":"塞弗林说得对，我应该避免抛头露面才是。","id":101},{"type":"text","text":"......所以，干脆装作不在好了。","id":102},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"安托医生，毕德曼已经有很多天没有露过面了......","id":103},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎，我们讲讲道理啊，那些家伙乱撒气把天灾信使揍了一顿，你让他怎么露面？","id":104},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"话、话是这么说......欸，等等，您要做什么......","id":105},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"——把门踹开啊？","id":106},{"type":"dialogue","name":"镇民","text":"欸？","id":107},{"type":"dialog","id":108},{"type":"text","text":"欸？","id":109},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":110},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别看我样，我也是能徒手干掉源石虫的——！","id":111},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"毕德曼，你在的吧？抱歉我不太清楚房间内的布置，麻烦你离门远一点哦！","id":112},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"躲不开的话，干脆防御吧！防御！双手交叉！","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"嘿——！","id":114},{"type":"dialog","id":115},{"type":"character","id":116},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"1","g":"1","b":"1","afrom":"0","rfrom":"0","gfrom":"0","bfrom":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":117},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.5","block":"false","id":118},{"type":"playsound","key":"$char_emp","volume":"0.9","id":119},{"type":"camerashake","duration":"1","xstrength":"10","ystrength":"12","vibrato":"30","randomness":"90","fadeout":"true","block":"true","id":120},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":121},{"type":"dialog","id":122},{"type":"text","text":"......罗德岛干员，安托。","id":123},{"type":"text","text":"她不由分说地找到我，为了寻求我的帮助。","id":124},{"type":"text","text":"我......我为什么要帮她？","id":125},{"type":"text","text":"在一座铁定要玩完的城镇里开设临时诊所救治感染者，这有什么好处？","id":126},{"type":"text","text":"对了......她是在利用我的愧疚心。不然她没有必要找上我这么一个犯了错的天灾信使。","id":127},{"type":"text","text":"我......","id":128},{"type":"text","text":"我没有拒绝的理由，塞弗林暗示我，这是改善我和居民关系的机会。","id":129},{"type":"text","text":"大概吧，我是这么和自己说的。","id":130},{"type":"text","text":"所以我去了。","id":131},{"type":"dialog","id":132},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":133},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/11/Avg_bg_bg_ltalley.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":134},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":135},{"type":"text","text":"......不早了。","id":136},{"type":"text","text":"我干嘛要工作得这么努力......","id":137},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069#4","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"啊......","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/8/8c/Avg_avg_npc_069_4.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"character","id":141},{"type":"text","text":"......看吧。他们见到我还是一副见到瘟神的表情。","id":142},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_069","id":143},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"毕德曼......谢谢你帮了托尔和塞弗林伯父。","id":144,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_069_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"不少没能躲开天灾范围的商旅也被困在了沃伦姆德，我们急需了解天灾的你帮助我们......","id":145,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_069_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"有些不理智的镇民做了不好的事情，但毕德曼先生您也在这里住了很久了，希望您能理解。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_069_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塔佳娜","text":"请好好休息。","id":147,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/2/23/Avg_avg_npc_069_1.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":148},{"type":"character","id":149},{"type":"text","text":"搞什么......来这套啊。","id":150},{"type":"text","text":"......算了。","id":151},{"type":"text","text":"明天还要帮安托搬箱子......今天还是早点休息吧。","id":152},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":155},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":156},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":157},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"喔，毕德曼，你很努力，这样我们的辟谣工作也能更加顺利。","id":158,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":159},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......我说过我对烟过敏吧。","id":160},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":161},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"你的私人空间在楼上，这里是公共区域。","id":162,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":163},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"辟谣？","id":164},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":165},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"帮你一把。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"......但相对的，我希望你也能帮帮我们。安托医生毕竟是个外人，你才是自己人。","id":167,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":168},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"——半个自己人。","id":169},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":170},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"好好......近期我们将会实施紧急时期物资管制方案，但是......","id":171,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"十二音街道的物资会是个大问题。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"新来了不少感染者难民......大都是商人和旅客，他们没能来得及逃离天灾范围。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"他们无法翻过满是活性源石结晶的大裂谷，别无选择，都追上了这座城镇。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"沃伦姆德可没有接纳那么多人的余裕......","id":176},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"见死不救也不行，事后没法交代。","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"所以我们暂且把他们都带去十二音街道那边了，住房勉强可以靠临时帐篷解决，但是食物......","id":179,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"我们还是得优先沃伦姆德的合法居民，然后，才是人道主义救援。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"很合理。他们会理解的。","id":182},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_066","id":183},{"type":"dialogue","name":"塞弗林","text":"会理解吗......但愿吧。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/41/Avg_avg_npc_066_1.png"},{"type":"character","id":185},{"type":"dialog","id":186},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":187},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/b/bb/Avg_bg_bg_ltroom.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":188},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......","id":190},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......信？谁进了我的房间，是塞弗林那家伙吗......","id":191},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"这是——","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"危机合约？","id":193},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"playsound","key":"$doorknockquite","volume":"0.6","id":195},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":196},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"谁？","id":197},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不要开门，就这样听我说。","id":198},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......","id":199},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......事到如今，还要找我做什么？","id":200},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎呀......别这么警惕，我们只是在试图挽回一些事情。","id":201},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你看，我也没做好，我应该早点抵达沃伦姆德的，结果我也失败了。","id":202},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你“本来”想做什么？","id":203},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"如果可能的话，我应该解决掉那场婚礼的问题，以确保沃伦姆德有足够多的人手应对天灾——","id":204},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"结果就不提了，我们谈谈现在。","id":205},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......随你们的便，我知道你的行事方针，但是没必要叫上我。","id":206},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎......你和那个感染者医生很熟。","id":207},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"——","id":208},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你该不会——","id":209},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"喔，你能第一反应就想到这么阴暗的可能性？早说了嘛，你该同意的。","id":210},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你不该把无辜的人安排到计划之内——安托她是个好医生！","id":211},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我知道，我当然知道，诶，谁没有被道德和良心束缚的时候呢？","id":212},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但现在我们别无选择，至少我能保证这件事之后，沃伦姆德会引起“足够多的关注”。","id":213},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你想引罗德岛过来......？","id":214},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哎呀......在我们众多的合作方里，罗德岛根本排不上号哦，至少表面如此。","id":215},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我们可不能指望他们能救下一整座城镇。","id":216},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"那么......你想要的就是暴乱本身。","id":217},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我会在高塔那边找找借口，只有点燃一把火，那些不问世事的贵族才会看清地面上的惨剧。","id":218},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"唉，有时候我真的无法分辨，他们是腐败到不在乎民间疾苦，还是单纯的离地面太远，远到不食人间烟火。","id":219},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"可、可这样会死很多人......","id":220},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"不这样也会死很多人。等到沃伦姆德的处境再糟一点，这座本来就一团乱麻的城镇有的是理由内讧。","id":221},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"更别提......跟上沃伦姆德的队伍中，混了一批比较特别的感染者。他们是武装分子，是反抗者，他们一定会带来争斗的。","id":222},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"既然如此，不如让我们来提前铺好路，尽可能少死点人。","id":223},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......","id":224},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别这么忧虑，轮不到你我去做这件事，也许是一个嫉妒的青年，也许是一个顽固的皮鞋匠，然后，只需要一场火灾......","id":225},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......你！","id":226},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这是你赎罪的机会，引导这场暴乱。","id":227},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"该死......躲在幕后看着无辜的人受苦受难，这样就行了吗！？","id":228},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"欸，这种无聊的道德选择让游刃有余的人去做，我是不会犹豫的。完全不会。","id":229},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"除非我要杀的全是好人，救的全是坏人。但天知道谁是好人谁是坏人。","id":230},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"以及，不要误会了，我才不会躲在幕后，口口声声必要的牺牲自己却不去送死，那是哪门子阴谋家？","id":231},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"在做这种权衡的时候，我已经罪该万死，所以“这一次牺牲”，我会给自己做个了结，这是我的规矩。","id":232},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我一定会死在这场暴乱里，死得其所。","id":233},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你......你疯了！？","id":234},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"啊对了，如果你答应我参与计划，你也会死。","id":235},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别担心，客观上你帮助了沃伦姆德，你赎罪了，主观上你为自己的罪行以死谢罪，两清，多好？","id":236},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"更别提害死感染者这件事，也不是你亲手做的嘛。你最大的罪行不过就是“纵容”，或是你的“赞同”。不算什么。","id":237},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"我们都在犯罪。不过不是因为行动而犯罪，是因为放弃行动而犯罪，有很多人都是这样犯罪的......","id":238},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"意识不到的时候，他们悲天悯人，意识到自己也是犯罪者后，他们走投无路。","id":239},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"所以我做事比较干脆，直接干掉自己。","id":240},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"好好想想吧。","id":241},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"这一切......都是为了更多的生命。","id":242},{"type":"dialog","id":243},{"type":"playsound","key":"$rungeneral","volume":"0.6","id":244},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":245},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"等等！","id":246},{"type":"dialog","id":247},{"type":"character","id":248},{"type":"playsound","key":"$dooropenquite","text":"","id":249},{"type":"dealy","time":"1","id":250},{"type":"text","text":"......","id":251},{"type":"text","text":"打开门的时候，走廊空无一人。","id":252},{"type":"text","text":"地上有冰晶......看来他并不是那么轻松地抵达这里，也是，毕竟他在附近城邦的计划多半失败了。","id":253},{"type":"text","text":"但......我不在乎他之前在计划什么......他不会亲自去找罗德岛的麻烦，但他说的对。","id":254},{"type":"text","text":"现在的沃伦姆德太不稳定了。","id":255},{"type":"text","text":"为了......更多的生命。","id":256},{"type":"text","text":"我干嘛要这么做？","id":257},{"type":"text","text":"本来就不是我的错，安托医生对我很好，我不需要为了一个假设的结果去赎什么罪......","id":258},{"type":"text","text":"我......我不需要。对的。暴乱不会到来的，沃伦姆德会度过这个难关的。","id":259},{"type":"text","text":"明天还要帮安托医生搬箱子.......明天要把这件事告诉她。只要不发生大规模暴乱，他说的话就都是放屁。","id":260},{"type":"text","text":"但如果......如果这些人真的因为饥荒和寒冷闹起内讧......我该......","id":261},{"type":"text","text":"不，至少她一定要幸免于难......安托医生她......没必要牺牲。","id":262},{"type":"text","text":"没错。","id":263},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"对了。","id":264},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......原来你没走，神出鬼没的家伙。","id":265},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"如果那个感染者医生真的死于非命......你会怎么对待你的私人感情和工作问题？","id":266},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......就算你想引发问题，也可以不通过安托的死来做到。","id":267},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"嚯......你帮我？你帮我就真的只是纯粹的犯罪了，这么不想让那个医生出事？","id":268},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":".......","id":269},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但我要提醒你一句，再提醒你一次。","id":270},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"感染者之死“不会是我安排谁去做”，我只是无比确定“那些感染者迟早会捅出篓子”。","id":271},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"别这么瞪我，你要是真想救下那个医生也不是不可以，前提是你做得到。","id":272},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......你似乎很确定感染者会出事，托尔。平时是那副好孩子嘴脸，为什么现在这么坚决地认定事情会往最坏的方向发展？","id":273},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"因为一定会发生。这种事情也不是第一次，过去我只是旁观，如今我身在其中。","id":274},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你应该和你的父亲商量，还有那个跟着你的小姑娘......你不该这么......","id":275},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"既然你这么富有人道主义精神......那建议你一步都不要离开那个医生喔。","id":276},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"反正......你可以小看我，毕竟我光是为了逃离追兵就煞费苦心。","id":277},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"啧啧，在冰天雪地里用冰雪法术掩盖自己，现在快被自己的源石技艺冻死了。","id":278},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"但不要小看现在的沃伦姆德孕育出的可能性。最糟糕的可能性。","id":279},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"哦......你会杀我？","id":280},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"你不会的。甚至到时候，为了能尽快让某一方妥协，你会主动帮助另一方。","id":281},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"未必。托尔瓦尔德......不管你心目中的人选是谁，你都是帮凶，你犯下死罪。","id":282},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"好、好......到时候你可以看着办，但不是现在。","id":283},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"......以及，我还得谢谢你。我原本的想法是把“这个”随便交给一个义愤填膺的非感染者，然后等着事情发生。","id":284},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"......这是，施术单元的核心，你从哪儿找来的？","id":285},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"留声机，那台留声机。看见了吗？","id":286},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"事成之后，我会在那里等你。","id":287},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"那里是我的坟墓，哈哈......这么一看，还挺近的。","id":288},{"type":"dialogue","name":"毕德曼","text":"你怕了。","id":289},{"type":"dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"总会害怕的。","id":290},{"type":"dialog","id":291},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":292},{"type":"character","id":293},{"type":"image","id":294}],"characters":["毕德曼","塞弗林","？？？","镇民","塔佳娜"]}